Thank you sweetheart.

501
00:32:27,629 --> 00:32:29,129
Now then, dear,

502
00:32:29,130 --> 00:32:31,632
I'll be back,
in two to three hours.

503
00:32:31,633 --> 00:32:33,133
Don't rush, darling,
take your time.

504
00:32:33,134 --> 00:32:35,636
Bye, bye daddy.
Bye, sweetheart.

