00:32:35,637 --> 00:32:37,638
Now as to the notes
of our last meeting...

506
00:32:51,653 --> 00:32:53,154
feed the kitty

507
00:32:57,659 --> 00:33:00,161
don't you ever bring a full bottle?

508
00:33:12,173 --> 00:33:13,174
Clear the court.

